  <entry>
    <title>Pure主题使用Katex渲染Latex公式</title>
    <link href="http://happylzyy.github.io/2021/08/06/how-to-render-latex-equation-code-with-katex/"/>
    <id>http://happylzyy.github.io/2021/08/06/how-to-render-latex-equation-code-with-katex/</id>
    <published>2021-08-06T06:47:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-06T07:40:59.790Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="安装依赖插件"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#安装依赖插件"></a> 安装依赖插件</h4><p>先卸载原先的渲染插件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm uninstall hexo-renderer-marked --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再安装新的渲染插件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-markdown-it-plus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文章启用mathjax"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#文章启用mathjax"></a> 文章启用Mathjax</h4><p>需要写公式的文章开头加入</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">mathjax:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="使用新版本katex"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#使用新版本katex"></a> 使用新版本Katex</h4><p>主题中使用的旧版本Katex有分数横线不显示的bug，升级最新版本可以完美解决</p><p>打开<code>head.ejs</code>文件，该文件位于<code>themes/pure/layout/_common/</code>，找到</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.9.0/dist/katex.min.css&quot;</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改为</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.12.0/dist/katex.min.css&quot;</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h4 id=&quot;安装依赖插件&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;markdownIt-Anchor&quot; href=&quot;#安装依赖插件&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 安装依赖插件&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;先卸载原先的渲染插件&lt;/p&gt;
